{"000-section": {"000-title": "Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana to be Implemented from April 1, 2016", "001-normal": "The government has empaneled 11 non-life insurance companies including the state-owned specialized agriculture insurer Agriculture Insurance Company for providing Fasal Bima to the farmers.", "002-normal": "Under the [Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana](https://sarkariyojana.com/pradhan-mantri-fasal-bima-yojana/), the farmers needs to pay a premium based on \u201cone season one premium\u201d. To get the crops insured, the farmers will need to pay 1.5% of the cost of the crop as premium for Rabi crops and 2% for the Kharif crops.", "003-normal": "The existing [crop insurance scheme](https://sarkariyojana.com/tag/crop-insurance-schemes-in-india/) of AIC will be merged into the PMFBY."}}